ML Requirements:**
- User verification system
- Geographic restrictions
- Transaction monitoring
- Suspicious activity reporting
- Data retention policies

**Legal Framework:**
- Terms of service and privacy policy
- Regulatory compliance (varies by jurisdiction)
- Market manipulation prevention
- Dispute resolution procedures
- Insurance coverage for platform risks

### 4.4 Enterprise & Partnerships

**White-Label Solutions:**
- Customizable platform for enterprises
- API-first architecture
- Brand customization options
- Dedicated infrastructure
- SLA guarantees

**Data Partnerships:**
- Sports data providers (ESPN, Reuters)
- Financial data feeds (Bloomberg, Yahoo Finance)
- News aggregation services
- Social sentiment analysis
- Weather and event APIs

**Integration Partners:**
- Wallet providers
- Exchange integrations
